Have you updated to iOS 12?

• Now Siri can answer "How busy is the Walmart store?"
Go to Services > Store Finder > Choose a Store > Make this my store > Tap Add to Siri

• If you've used Walmart Pay, you can ask Siri to "Open Walmart Pay!"
Go to Settings > Siri & Search > All Shortcuts, and then tap "+"

Have you updated to iOS 12?
• Now Siri can answer "How busy is the Walmart store?"

Go to Settings > Siri & Search > All Shortcuts, and then tap "+"
